Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在位于美国宇航局埃姆斯研究中心的垂直射击靶场 重现了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are attempting to recreate the early impacts on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上这些最初的碰撞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}by using the Vertical Gun Range at NASA's Ames Research Centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞满整个大房间的是一个巨大的轻质气体炮\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's a warehouse-sized room housing a massive light gas gun
