Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个纵向的发射器指向的特别目标\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The vertical gun launches projectiles at specified targets
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个真空室\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}inside a vacuum chamber.
