Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以使这个系统非常的相似于\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}makes it really realistic in terms of comparison
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球表面所发生的那些\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to what happened on the surface of Earth
