Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到真空室之中 而我们使用这个是因为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}into the chamber, and we use this because
