Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近发现了某些彗星存在于一个不寻常之处\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}recently discovered comets in an unlikely place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是火星和木星间的小行星带\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Asteroid Belt located between Mars and Jupiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些相对温暖的彗星也许拥有着与地球一样的水\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These warmer ice-bearing bodies may have the same water as Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:22:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们在太阳系内部运转更靠近太阳\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because they were all formed in the inner solar system, which is closer to the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人惊异的更多证据表明\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What's more, startling new evidence suggests
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些不寻常的彗星不但可能给地球带来了水\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that these unusual comets may not only have delivered water to Earth,
