Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.82,0:22:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带来那些基本生命单元\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with the building blocks of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命的起源\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The origin of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.13,0:22:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始终是地球的一个迷\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It remains one of the most puzzling and controversial questions about our Planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.66,0:22:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以确定的是在39亿年前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One thing is certain: 3.9 billion years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.49,0:22:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相比之下人类历史只是非常短的一段时间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}humans would have lasted for only a brief moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.85,0:22:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大气含有大量二氧化碳 水蒸气\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Earth's atmosphere consisted of carbon dioxide, water vapour,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及少量氮气 却没有氧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a little nitrogen, but no oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.66,0:23:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是原始生命如何才能在这样环境下生存？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yet, could primitive life have endured in such an environment?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有确切的证明约43亿年前的环境能产生生命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We have no firm evidence that there was life 4.3 billion years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.43,0:23:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们相信这些都是可能的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but we think now that the conditions were possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些地球上最古老的化石\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The oldest fossils on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.44,0:23:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形成于大约37到39亿年前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}only date back 3.7 to 3.9 billion years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.26,0:23:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些人认为这些最原始的生命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Some believe that these remains once evolved
