Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里大气中的化合物在能量作用下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There, atmospheric chemicals and energy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形成了含有一些基本氨基酸的汤\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}formed a primordial soup of amino acids,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命的基本材料\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the essential elements of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.53,0:23:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是万一这些原始生命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But, could the building blocks of life
