Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是天外来物？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Perhaps from an extraterrestrial object?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.69,0:23:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括各种氨基酸的有机物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Meteorites contain organic materials, including amino acids.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.27,0:23:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因某些原因形成于太阳系某处\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They were formed somehow in the earlier solar system.
