Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.45,0:24:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播种地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so they would help seed a planet
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.23,0:24:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造了生命起源的条件\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so the conditions for life could begin to exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.34,0:24:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彗星和小行星可能带来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Comets and asteroids probably brought
