Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.25,0:25:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在于地球上一些最不适宜生存的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in some of the most uninhabitable places on Earth.
