Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.12,0:26:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球生命的最初20亿年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that for the first 2 billion years of this planet's living history,
